            . I took the prisoner, and have the handkerchief.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I took a walk on Tower-hill - the gentleman accused me of this, and pushed me into a shop; I said I had not the handkerchief - he saw it in another man's hand, and let him go about his business; I never had it.</p>
